    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 1
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: 'EVENTSYSTEM PIPELINE


    01  RadarPipeClient receives the latest pointer
    frame.


    02  RadarFrameDispatcher publishes it on Unity''s main thread.


    03
    RadarInputModule creates PointerEventData per TrackId.


    04  EventSystem.RaycastAll
    queries Graphic, Physics and Physics2D raycasters.


    05  ExecuteEvents invokes
    standard pointer, drag, drop and scroll handlers.


    Try the controls and
    drag both world targets.'
